      <title>今年汽车被收回数量为何激增</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-16/why-car-repossessions-are-surging-this-year-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年上半年汽车回购量飙升，这表明随着美联储考虑降息，消费者的困境正在加剧。根据 Cox Automotive 的数据，截至目前，2024 年的回购量与去年同期相比增长了 23%。Claire Ballentine 有更多报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-16/why-car-repossessions-are-surging-this-year-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 20:48:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
